caseTitle: Raja Rabnawaz v. Federation of Pakistan & others
authorJudge: MR. JUSTICE TASSADUQ HUSSAIN JILLANI, HCJ
tagline: The Court directs the learned Attorney General for Pakistan to assist as regards the consequences of any further delay in the holding of Local Government Elections in the Cantonment Areas and if the Local Government Elections in the Cantonment Areas can be held under the existing law.
